# The wiki_engine is a byte-exact engine: its source and test fixtures must have
# deterministic line endings across platforms. Pin everything under scripts/ to LF so
# git's autocrlf never flips fixture EOLs on checkout (which would break byte-level
# fixtures and any EOL-specific assertion). CRLF handling is still covered by the
# in-memory CRLF round-trip test.
* text eol=lf
